comment.author: 51979177@N02
comment._content: www.flickr.com/photos/51979177@N02/9704930401/ I'm not sure, but I don't think this is her...all these flappers look the same! nla.gov.au/nla.news-article84901344 another pic of Harriet Bennet...still don't think it's her...but not 100% sure nla.gov.au/nla.pic-vn3674331 another one...might have to call in a phrenologist! nla.gov.au/nla.pic-vn3674331 this NLA pic indicates Harriet Bennet didn't have dark eyes...whereas this woman appears to have dark eyes...but maybe that's due to the lighting. I'd also suggest Harriet Bennet had more of a top lip and a slightly longer nose than this woman, but I could be wrong...maybe that's due to the angle at which the pics were taken.
